{"tid":2218064,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"粉嶺被捕手足保釋申請被拒 案件押後至11月20日","createTime":"2020-09-26T02:48:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T22:34:26.000Z","uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f4450c31d857c4e11084b1742c57388ba92c1e","tid":2218064,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T02:48:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F9827&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu4tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=af42235c\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9827</a><br />\n<br />\n#屯門裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#張潔宜署理主任裁判官<br />\n#20200924粉嶺<br />\n#新案件<br />\n<br />\n呂<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n1. 無牌管有槍械 (違反火器及彈藥條例 第13條）<br />\n<br />\n被指於粉嶺某一單位內管有1支手槍型的胡椒球槍及4支氣槍<br />\n<br />\n2. 未經許可輸入戰略物品 (違反進出口條例 第6A(2)條）<br />\n<br />\n被指於粉嶺某一單位非按照工業貿易署署長發出的進口許可證輸入戰略物品，即1件避彈衣及15個防毒面具<br />\n<br />\n3. 管有攻擊性武器 (違反簡易程序治罪條例 第17條）<br />\n<br />\n被指於粉嶺某一單位內管有2把大約30cm長軍刀及1支伸縮棍<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n被告在第一次警誡時保持緘默，其後被告承認有關物屬於他，只屬收藏用，或是打Wargame時候使用，亦承認在網上售賣<br />\n<br />\n投訴：<br />\n<br />\n被告不只一次被國安署威脅坦白承認，否則會起訴被告母親及姐姐<br />\n<br />\n律師多次致電詢問被告位置，但警方沒有回答，警方回覆要先詢問被告是否需要律師<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n裁判官拒絕准予被告保釋<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至11月20日0930於粉嶺裁判法院第一庭再訊"},{"pid":"a805228240032b4e7bf04a4169df95f8049f2d79","tid":2218064,"uid":9566,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T02:49:49.000Z","msg":"又一未審先判"},{"pid":"d3f9159b946ac70f0536fcb390f0ce1a3f516a74","tid":2218064,"uid":44209,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T02:49:59.000Z","msg":"又係威脅人唔講就搞佢屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286205776604200bf2b91cf1fe69d012d7a10c65","tid":2218064,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T02:53:25.000Z","msg":"War game 友要小心啲"},{"pid":"6c614fe5a418069b5ac8bd3f3804b452208efdd1","tid":2218064,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T02:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b686e33f0ce7b408e40d4b2b9bb5ab3d7bb7e5","tid":2218064,"uid":248120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T02:57:13.000Z","msg":"紅底官又DLLM"},{"pid":"be8d7937d4f6a563b55f547d3482e86171763fbb","tid":2218064,"uid":146944,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T02:59:31.000Z","msg":"又搞人地屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7196e3913498e9c33cf3a51516a1e0bfd15b200f","tid":2218064,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be8d7937d4f6a563b55f547d3482e86171763fbb","tid":2218064,"uid":146944,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T02:59:31.000Z","msg":"又搞人地屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T03:03:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf5c356df58600b9e70469d1956fc538c61fd8a","tid":2218064,"uid":254788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T03:06:06.000Z","msg":"法治未死dllm"},{"pid":"fe6a1fe285b485a95d91f14c6487ec673e5e8004","tid":2218064,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T03:08:28.000Z","msg":"你如果係一個活躍放社交媒體嘅黃絲就唔好玩氣槍啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2217203\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2217203</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":